òSpike
November 12th 1998 - March 26th 2010
Lithe spirit racing along the sand
Forever treasured, loved and missed

In memory of all the dogs that have ever
walked on Instow beach and in particular of
REBEL the German Shepherd, who died
aged 12 on April 17th 1996, just a few days
after his last holiday here.  Sit here in peace and
enjoy the view that unlike us, goes on forever.

LABSA
Our beloved Lou Bear, German girl, who lit up our life and
the lives of those who knew her.  It was live at first sight
a love that will stay with us always.
May you continue to chase sticks in heaven with a smile
on your face, as you did here on Instow beach."û
